    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed or flagged as epistemic gaps with documented justification. Seven factors assessed with achieved levels below required levels; six factors not assessed due to data availability constraints at MRL 5. Monte Carlo UQ performed for primary input parameters. Validation metric within combined uncertainty band at 4 of 5 operating points. Assessment team accepts the package subject to gap closure plan for model form, model inputs, use error, test samples, and equivalency factors prior to regulatory submission.",
